U.K.’s FTSE 100 Index Drops for Third Day as Basic-Materials Shares Fall

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-05-06T07:48:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/stocks-decline-for-third-day-in-london-as-basic-materials-shares-retreat.html
U.K. stocks fell for a third day,
extending the FTSE 100 Index’s weekly decline, as basic-
materials companies dropped with commodities.  The FTSE 100 slid 0.4 percent to 5,895.95 at 8:47 a.m. in
 London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
